nents of my approach and results?": "Our approach involves developing an adaptive attention mechanism specifically tailored for mobile UI screens. We will tailor the model architecture to handle the unique characteristics of UI screens, integrate advanced adaptive attention mechanisms, and develop specialized datasets with annotations for referring and grounding tasks. We will use metrics such as accuracy, precision, recall, and F1-score to evaluate the model\'s performance. The expected outcomes include a more efficient and accurate vision-language model for mobile UIs, capable of performing a wide range of tasks and improving user interaction and accessibility."\n}\n```', role='assistant', tool_calls=None, function_call=None, provider_specific_fields=None)
