ed research and its significance.\n   - Expected impact on the field of machine learning and its applications in mobile user interfaces.\n\nThis detailed research proposal outlines the key components of the proposed approach and provides a comprehensive plan for developing a sophisticated system that can understand and interact with mobile UI screens using LVLMs.", role='assistant', tool_calls=None, function_call=None, provider_specific_fields=None)'.
